.distribution
Shareware
.description
A blackjack simulation program with the ability to simulate nearly any
casino blackjack game in the world.  Allows the use of the most popular
playing strategies and modifications to them.  Has color coded strategy
tables to enhance the learning of the strategy.  Tracks basic statistics
such as number of hands played, bankroll limits, casino profitability and
others.  Allows from 1 to 7 players, including the computer.  Has online
help, a demo mode, and a special practice mode.  
